HEADWORD: green-blindness
<hw>green-blindness</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A defect of color vision
characterized by inability to distinguish green and
purplish-red.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> deuteranopia, daltonism.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

